title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - Concorde - Start the engines
description:
In this video we are going to look at which steps are required to turn on the 4 engines of the Concorde before you can start your flight. Having the checklist build-in makes it a bit easier although for some items we need to search a bit.

If you would like to try Concorde yourself download it from the site below:
https://www.justflight.com/product/dc-designs-concorde-microsoft-flight-simulator
